{"tid":831863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【AA搶客搶到顛】屯門新盤 情侶路過也中槍","createTime":"2018-09-22T10:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T01:15:58.000Z","uid":122377,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9908bf76ae5b896964e51f3019267107f009e905","tid":831863,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"中資萬科旗下屯門山旯旮新盤上源昨日開價，首批231伙，當中最平呎價不足萬元，成為近一年內呎價最平新盤。項目設於長沙灣的售樓廠，今日為首個開放的周末，下午兩點左右，售樓廠現場有近百人排隊睇樓。<br />\n<br />\n由於下午上源售樓廠一帶有大批代理推銷，現場偶爾出現代理爭客情景，一對年輕男女路過售樓廠門口，被大約十名代理一湧而上包圍著，即時有人起哄叫囂，該名女子被數人互相推撞，更被撞到垃圾筒旁邊，場面混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180922/58711784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180922%2F58711784&d=ApFr65%2F7CQXVI7Zo3g%2FMeROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=606b8866\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180922%2F58711784&h=43535ccc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180922/58711784</a><br />\n<br />\n條片笑撚到仆街 班AA餓左幾撚耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ef83ca38f73639c7bd41d34badeb28db96e50c","tid":831863,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:31:50.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗開兩個post"},{"pid":"9f596d314442753537e18b4cfd74459a3974a343","tid":831863,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"39ef83ca38f73639c7bd41d34badeb28db96e50c","tid":831863,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:31:50.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗開兩個post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:38:06.000Z","msg":"咁係好笑呀ma<br />\n班AA係折撚墮呀ma <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e580f